race.comment: This isn't strong. MATERIAL MADAM (6) is holding a decent level of form, and she's suited over the longer sprint back on grass. Has an awkward gate but has a 2kg claim today and that weight relief may prove the difference. She rates the best chance. MYWORDIS (3) found more like his best finding a place on the synthetic and Pires is reunited today. Has each way claims in this line up. NIGHT ACTION (4) tries hard and finds a touch easier. With average luck from the awkward gate he can get into the finish. ETHICAL DILEMMA (1) has been plainer his last two but finds easier than last time and three back he missed a whisker at Hobart. Darmanin rides today and that sparks interest.
